(239, 1, '2017-04-13 14:43:44', '2017-04-13 14:43:44', '<span style="background: white; color: black; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\';">iPhone 6s - Take everything that made the previous generation great, and advance it to a new level. They’re made with 7000 Series aluminium, the strongest alloy we’ve ever used in an iPhone. They both feature Retina HD displays made from the strongest cover glass used on any smartphone in the world. And now they’re available in an elegant new rose gold ﬁnish.</span>\r\n<h4>MORE INFORMATION</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Lithium-ion battery providing talk-time of 14 hours on 3G networks and standby time of 240 hours</li>\r\n 	<li>1 year manufacturer warranty for device and 6 months manufacturer warranty for in-box accessories including batteries from the date of purchase</li>\r\n</ul>', 'iPhone 6S GOLD', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>12MP primary camera with auto focus, flash and 5MP front facing camera</li>\r\n 	<li>4.7-inch (11.4 centimeters) Retina HD 3D-touch capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n 	<li>1334 x 750 pixels resolution and 326 ppi pixel density</li>\r\n 	<li>iOS v9 operating system with A9 chip 64-bit architecture processor</li>\r\n 	<li>2GB RAM, 64GB internal memory and single nano SIM</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'iphone-6s-gold', '', '', '2017-04-14 12:51:47', '2017-04-14 12:51:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mcom/?post_type=product&#038;p=239', 0, 'product', '', 0),
