(309, 1, '2017-04-14 14:18:20', '2017-04-14 14:18:20', '<span style="background: white; color: #212121; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; font-size: 10.5pt;">If you are looking for a high-end laptop with plenty of features and high-performance, then what you need to be doing is investing in this Apple MacBook Pro. Stylish and powerful, this laptop delivers seamless multitasking and lag-free computing for maximum efficiency and productivity.</span>\n<h4>MORE INFORMATION</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li>2.0GHz dual-core Intel Core i5 processor</li>\n 	<li>Turbo Boost up to 3.1GHz</li>\n 	<li>8GB 1866MHz memory</li>\n 	<li>256GB PCIe-based SSD<sup>1</sup></li>\n 	<li>Intel Iris Graphics 540</li>\n 	<li>Two Thunderbolt 3 ports</li>\n</ul>', 'MAC BOOK PRO- 13inch', '<ul><li>2.0GHz Processor&nbsp; 256GB Storage</li><li>FOR MORE INFO:&nbsp;&nbsp; <span id="_mce_caret" data-mce-bogus="true"><a href="http://localhost/mcom/product/mac-book-pro-13inch/" data-wplink-url-error="true" data-mce-href="http://localhost/mcom/product/mac-book-pro-13inch/">http://localhost/mcom/product/mac-book-pro-13inch/</a></span></li></ul>', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '230-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-04-14 14:18:20', '2017-04-14 14:18:20', '', 230, 'http://localhost/mcom/230-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(252, 1, '2017-04-13 19:33:52', '2017-04-13 19:33:52', 'The Apple iPhone 7 Plus is the best iPhone yet. It is extremely lightweight at just 188 grams and incredibly thin at 7.3mm. This is the first iPhone which comes with built-in stereo speakers. This makes watching movies and videos on it a real joy. The iPhone 7 Plus features a sleek body that is crafted out of spaceship-grade Aluminum. It comes in a vibrant Red color.\r\n\r\nMORE INFORMATION\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Colour Family Red</li>\r\n 	<li>SIM Size Nano SIM</li>\r\n 	<li>Network Supported GSM / UMTS / LTE</li>\r\n 	<li>Display Type Retina HD</li>\r\n 	<li>Multitouch Yes</li>\r\n 	<li>Operating System iOS 10</li>\r\n 	<li>Processor Chipset A10 Fuion chip</li>\r\n</ul>', 'iPhone 7+ - RED(128GB)', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Display Resolution 1920 x 1080</li>\r\n 	<li>Screen Size Range 5.0 - 5.5</li>\r\n 	<li>Screen Size 5.5 inches</li>\r\n 	<li>Rear Camera Resolution (MP) 12 MP</li>\r\n 	<li>Front Camera Resolution (MP) 7 MP</li>\r\n 	<li>Internal Memory (GB) 128 GB</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'iphone-7-red', '', '', '2017-04-14 13:21:26', '2017-04-14 13:21:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mcom/?post_type=product&#038;p=252', 0, 'product', '', 0),
