(257, 1, '2017-04-13 19:48:59', '2017-04-13 19:48:59', 'World-class noise cancellation makes quiet sound quieter and music sound better\r\n\r\nBluetooth pairing for wireless connection to your iOS devices\r\n\r\nVolume-optimized EQ provides balanced audio performance at any volume\r\n\r\nLithium-ion battery delivers to 20 hours of wireless listening per charge\r\n\r\nNoise-rejecting dual-microphone system provides clear calls, even in windy or noisy environments\r\n\r\nPremium materials offer light weight and solid comfort for all-day listening\r\n\r\nFree Bose Connect app helps you manage your paired devices and gives you a personalized experience\r\n<h4>MORE INFORMATION</h4>\r\nBluetooth Compatiblity: Bluetooth 2.0 Compatibility, Bluetooth 2.1, Bluetooth 3.0, Bluetooth 4.0\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'BOSE QUIET COMFORT', '<ul>\r\n 	<li> Active Noise Cancelling, Bluetooth</li>\r\n 	<li>With Mic, With Remote and Mic</li>\r\n 	<li>Inline Volume Control, Noise Cancelling</li>\r\n 	<li>Stereo Bluetooth, Wireless</li>\r\n 	<li>Form Factor: Over Ear</li>\r\n 	<li>Connections: Wireless</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bose-quiet-comfort', '', '', '2017-04-14 13:35:33', '2017-04-14 13:35:33', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mcom/?post_type=product&#038;p=257', 0, 'product', '', 1),
