(285, 1, '2017-04-14 04:25:25', '2017-04-14 04:25:25', 'Strap on the Apple Watch and stay connected throughout the day, always. This water-resistant smartwatch comes with a sturdy Ion-X glass display, a heart rate sensor, an accelerometer, an ambient light sensor and a gyroscope, making it perfect for both indoor and outdoor use. The built-in speaker and microphone let you conveniently make calls, right from your wrist.\r\n\r\nAdditional Details: This device\'s battery life lasts for up to 18 hours, including 45 minutes of using apps and a 30-minute workout with music playback, and checking time and notifications 90 times each. The battery life may vary based on usage. The Apple Watch app is required to use this device\'s smart functions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'APPLE WATCH SERIES 1-33MM- WHITE SPORT BAND', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Dual Core S1P processor for faster performance</li>\r\n 	<li>Track your activity and share them with your friends</li>\r\n 	<li>Heart-Rate Monitoring</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'apple-watch-series-1-33mm-white-sport-band', '', '', '2017-04-14 06:30:07', '2017-04-14 06:30:07', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mcom/?post_type=product&#038;p=285', 0, 'product', '', 0),
