(89, 1, '2017-03-25 07:38:33', '2017-03-25 07:38:33', '[huge_it_slider id="1"]\r\n\r\n<strong>ABOUT US</strong>\r\n\r\nIndian institute of Museum Management is affiliated with Museum AND Art E-Newsletter, a monthly publication reaching out to museum, archaeology, preservation/conservation and heritage professionals. The Newsletter is an accomplishment in the museum sphere which brings together information from around the world and disseminates information about Indian museums and cultural centres to international organisations and funding agencies. IIMM aims at bringing together scholars, students and museum professionals from around the globe to address the important archaeological, conservation and museological matters of the day.\r\n\r\nThe E-Newsletter through its coverage of events and happenings of the institute and other cultural centres helps the institute to collaborate with prominent Indian museums, archaeological and heritage centres to organise various workshops and programs so as to link theory to practice thus helping students to broaden their scope and knowledge.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-25 07:38:33', '2017-03-25 07:38:33', '', 34, 'http://localhost/iimm/2017/03/25/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(91, 1, '2017-03-25 08:19:21', '2017-03-25 08:19:21', '[wds id="1"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>ABOUT US</strong>\r\n\r\nIndian institute of Museum Management is affiliated with Museum AND Art E-Newsletter, a monthly publication reaching out to museum, archaeology, preservation/conservation and heritage professionals. The Newsletter is an accomplishment in the museum sphere which brings together information from around the world and disseminates information about Indian museums and cultural centres to international organisations and funding agencies. IIMM aims at bringing together scholars, students and museum professionals from around the globe to address the important archaeological, conservation and museological matters of the day.\r\n\r\nThe E-Newsletter through its coverage of events and happenings of the institute and other cultural centres helps the institute to collaborate with prominent Indian museums, archaeological and heritage centres to organise various workshops and programs so as to link theory to practice thus helping students to broaden their scope and knowledge.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-25 08:19:21', '2017-03-25 08:19:21', '', 34, 'http://localhost/iimm/2017/03/25/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(90, 1, '2017-03-25 08:05:52', '2017-03-25 08:05:52', '[huge_it_slider id="1"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>ABOUT US</strong>\r\n\r\nIndian institute of Museum Management is affiliated with Museum AND Art E-Newsletter, a monthly publication reaching out to museum, archaeology, preservation/conservation and heritage professionals. The Newsletter is an accomplishment in the museum sphere which brings together information from around the world and disseminates information about Indian museums and cultural centres to international organisations and funding agencies. IIMM aims at bringing together scholars, students and museum professionals from around the globe to address the important archaeological, conservation and museological matters of the day.\r\n\r\nThe E-Newsletter through its coverage of events and happenings of the institute and other cultural centres helps the institute to collaborate with prominent Indian museums, archaeological and heritage centres to organise various workshops and programs so as to link theory to practice thus helping students to broaden their scope and knowledge.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-25 08:05:52', '2017-03-25 08:05:52', '', 34, 'http://localhost/iimm/2017/03/25/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
